_sText: zm_deep_thought_nv This is a compact little map that we have had on our ZM server for a long time. It's quite old though so I took the time to spice it up a little bit with a couple more camping spots and some revisions on older ones. All in all it should be fun to play. Features: - Cubemaps - Radar Map - 64 Spawns The original version is called zm_deep_thought_remix and was made by archangel_505 some time ago. This is the second time I've released a map that had input from both of us in it. If you have questions or comments let me know.
